column1: $\tilde{F}_{ijk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j + f_i f_k + f_i + f_j f_k + f_j + f_k + 1}{36 \left(\omega_i + \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq& "$\tilde{F}_{ijk}^2\frac{f_i f_j - f_i f_k - f_j f_k - f_k}{36 \left(\omega_i + \omega_j - \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{ijk}^2\frac{- f_i f_j + f_i f_k - f_j f_k - f_j}{36 \left(\omega_i - \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{ijk}^2\frac{f_i f_j + f_i f_k + f_i - f_j f_k}{36 \left(\omega_i - \omega_j - \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\"

$\tilde{F}_{ijkk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j + f_i f_k^{2} + f_i + f_j f_k^{2} + f_j + f_k^{2} + 2 f_k \left(f_i f_j + f_i + f_j + 1\right) + 1}{8 \left(\omega_i + \omega_j + 2 \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq& "$\tilde{F}_{ijkk}^2\frac{2 f_i f_j f_k + f_i f_j - f_i f_k^{2} - f_j f_k^{2} - f_k^{2}}{8 \left(\omega_i + \omega_j - 2 \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{ijjk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j^{2} + f_i f_k + f_i + f_j^{2} f_k + f_j^{2} + 2 f_j \left(f_i f_k + f_i + f_k + 1\right) + f_k + 1}{8 \left(\omega_i + 2 \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{ijjk}^2- \frac{- f_i f_j^{2} + f_i f_k + f_j^{2} f_k + 2 f_j f_k \left(f_i + 1\right) + f_k}{8 \left(\omega_i + 2 \omega_j - \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{ijjk}^2\frac{- f_i f_j^{2} + 2 f_i f_j f_k + f_i f_k - f_j^{2} f_k - f_j^{2}}{8 \left(\omega_i - 2 \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{ijjk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j^{2} + 2 f_i f_j \left(f_k + 1\right) + f_i f_k + f_i - f_j^{2} f_k}{8 \left(- \omega_i + 2 \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{ijkk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j - f_i f_k^{2} + f_j f_k^{2} + 2 f_j f_k \left(f_i + 1\right) + f_j}{8 \left(\omega_i - \omega_j + 2 \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{ijkk}^2- \frac{f_i f_j + f_i f_k^{2} + 2 f_i f_k \left(f_j + 1\right) + f_i - f_j f_k^{2}}{8 \left(- \omega_i + \omega_j + 2 \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{iijk}^2- \frac{f_i^{2} f_j + f_i^{2} f_k + f_i^{2} + 2 f_i \left(f_j f_k + f_j + f_k + 1\right) + f_j f_k + f_j + f_k + 1}{8 \left(2 \omega_i + \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{iijk}^2- \frac{- f_i^{2} f_j + f_i^{2} f_k + 2 f_i f_k \left(f_j + 1\right) + f_j f_k + f_k}{8 \left(2 \omega_i + \omega_j - \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\" "$\tilde{F}_{iijk}^2- \frac{f_i^{2} f_j - f_i^{2} f_k + 2 f_i f_j \left(f_k + 1\right) + f_j f_k + f_j}{8 \left(2 \omega_i - \omega_j + \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq&" "$\tilde{F}_{iijk}^2\frac{f_i^{2} f_j + f_i^{2} f_k + f_i^{2} - 2 f_i f_j f_k - f_j f_k}{8 \left(2 \omega_i - \omega_j - \omega_k\right)}$ &Eq \\"
